":"2017-11-20T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下大家二月嘅羅浮宮同梵帝崗博物館係咪算淡季所以會少啲人？係網上search過依兩個地方都係多人到爆最好上網買定飛如果唔係起碼排一兩個鐘隊，但搵唔到如果二月旅遊淡季係咪都會，有無人試過依啲月份係咪會少啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前者唔洗後者要</blockquote><br />\n梵帝崗二月都咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16646075ee5f05eaf290e95cead8def79d235789","tid":474481,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"兩個都去過<br />\n後者記得網上買reserve飛<br />\n前者排隊的話小心小偷"},{"pid":"d88f9c5864cb67880a22596d67c373e0cc0bafe4","tid":474481,"uid":72702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個都去過<br />\n後者記得網上買reserve飛<br />\n前者排隊的話小心小偷</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53652b08d2632e8b58d5a2db9f597117cece272c","tid":474481,"uid":46018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"我8月去法國，一早去walk in 都唔係排左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後梵帝崗就因為太厭倦所以冇入去睇la，不過聽講就好爆，買定好d"},{"pid":"79c289e6025e88e3f108bf12172f1e96b0895057","tid":474481,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"羅浮宮非旺季唔多人<br />\n<br />\n你一開館入去基本上唔洗點排隊<br />\n<br />\n另外, 佢有個地下街入口, 怕多人可以係個度入, 人更少<br />\n<br />\n去過2次, 一早入去, 閘口無人CHECK飛 (仲要係金字塔入口), 我估D職員未返工<br />\n我見有D人無買飛直入 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梵帝崗就最好一早上網搞"},{"pid":"e38d0467b47049781b0ff69fd9feedd93435cb6b","tid":474481,"uid":72702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11